 'content': 'Valuation multiples in the SaaS industry can vary significantly '
            'based on market conditions and growth potential of the firms. As '
            'observed in recent trends, mid-2021 valuations were particularly '
            'high, with many high-growth SaaS companies achieving EV/EBITDA '
